import axios from'axios';// axios instance with default config
const api=axios.create({baseURL:'/api',timeout:15000,headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'}});// API endpoints
const endpoints={getIndicators:()=>api.get('/indicators'),// this is getting specific indicator data
